Sprout Lands asset notes
========================

Imported files in this repository:
- assets/tilesets/sprout-lands-grass.png
- assets/tilesets/sprout-lands-fences.png
- assets/tilesets/sprout-lands-water.png
- assets/sprites/sprout-lands-player.png

Original source:
- https://cupnooble.itch.io/sprout-lands-asset-pack

Mirror used to retrieve the exact free-pack files checked into this repo:
- https://github.com/perquis/sprout_lands

Author credit:
- Cup Nooble

Free version license text from the original pack page:
- This asset pack can be used in any non-commercial project.
- You may modify the assets as you wish.
- The free asset pack cannot be used in commercial projects.
- The free asset pack cannot be resold or redistributed, even if modified.

This repository keeps only the minimum files needed for the first playable slice and preserves attribution here for downstream reviewers.
